author: ghudson
msg: Use a cleverer method of computing the base file revision in FSFS.  To
compensate for being cleverer, do a better job of explaining what
we're doing in comments.
* subversion/libsvn_fs_fs/fs_fs.c (choose_delta_base): x&(x-1) flips
the rightmost set bit in x without the need for a loop, so use that.

author: xsteve
msg: * trunk/contrib/client-side/psvn/psvn.el:
- The sorting of the svn-status buffer is now optional
- This speeds up the M-x svn-status command
- However, the filelist is probably not correctly sorted
when this feature is used
- Added the svnstatus-mode-options-map
- The above mentioned sorting variable can be saved via
the new options mechanism.
- The options can be loaded again
